{"tid":858439,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過停敏感藥之後周身痕","createTime":"2018-10-11T21:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T22:11:21.000Z","uid":173398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0b816e6f862514fb354927c1916c5304d6262c0c","tid":858439,"uid":173398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T21:57:55.000Z","msg":"歐洲返香港之後開始皮膚敏感，屋企人介紹隻敏感藥叫zertine，其他名係cetirizine或者zyrtec，都係指同一隻藥<br />\n<br />\n一開始食就幾好，本來敏感嘅地方都無再痕(頸同背)<br />\n但食咗幾個月，近排開始停就出曬事，頸背痕到訓覺都唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ngoogle cetirizine withdrawal見好多外國人都話有類似經驗，有啲就話cut開粒藥然後循序漸進慢慢減，會冇cold turkey咁難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有冇人有經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e57a4a18cdd3d6643b462b9552832830e4901e9","tid":858439,"uid":42269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T22:11:21.000Z","msg":"隻藥只係暫時止痕，治標唔治本，唔食緊食痕"}]}